text: José Andrés Anchondo García (born 10 November 1962) is a Mexican archer. Anchondo competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics.Andrés Anchondo == References == Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican archers Category:Olympians for Mexico Category:People from Chihuahua (state)
